5
00:00:13,714 --> 00:00:16,721
difference. With a Hemisphere Light, you assign a light color to the top and a

6
00:00:16,721 --> 00:00:20,396
different color to the bottom. Each object's normals determine the color of the

7
00:00:20,396 --> 00:00:23,880
light it receives from this light source. If the normal points upward, the

8
