bottom color. Any direction in between gives a blend of these two colors. The

10
00:00:31,547 --> 00:00:33,887
idea is that you can assign the top color to be something like the sky, the

11
00:00:33,887 --> 00:00:37,660
bottom to be something like the surrounding terrain. It's basically a more

12
